data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT with the option to use $5,000 toward price reduction, closing costs or rate buy-down. **VA ASSUMABLE LOAN WITH 2.25% INTEREST RATE** Welcome to your dream home! This stunning two-story, 4 bedroom, 3 bath home offers the perfect blend of elegance and functionality. A new roof ensures peace of mind, while stainless steel appliances add a touch of modern sophistication to the spacious kitchen. Step outside to the inviting covered porch and soak in the tranquil views of the adjacent greenbelt. The outdoor oasis awaits with a refinished inground pool, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. Whether hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings, this home provides the ideal backdrop for making lasting memories.
